Hello. My name's Lilac.

510
00:21:26,375 --> 00:21:28,083
You saved me from Greed.

511
00:21:28,166 --> 00:21:29,166
Thank you.

512
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:34,333
[MAHIRU]
Kuro?

513
00:21:40,041 --> 00:21:42,458
